EDUCATIONAL PROJECT NOTICE:

This software was developed as a school project for the Software Project (SWP)
course at TGM - Die Schule der Technik. While the MIT License allows commercial
and private use, this project is primarily intended for educational purposes
and demonstration of software engineering principles.

The authors are students at TGM and created this project as part of their
curriculum in the 4BHWII class during the 2024/2025 academic year.

PROJECT COMPONENTS:

- Database Layer (MongoDB Integration): Emir Keser
- View Layer (Gradio Web Interface): Mateja Gvozdenac  
- Business Logic (Core Features): Paul Hinterbauer

TECHNICAL ARCHITECTURE:

This project implements Clean Architecture (Hexagonal Architecture) principles
with clear separation between:
- Ports (Abstract Interfaces) in contracts/ports.py
- Adapters (Concrete Implementations) in adapters/
- Business Logic (Core Domain) in business_logic/

