- Mateja Gvozdenac: mgvozdenac@student.tgm.ac.at
- Paul Hinterbauer: phinterbauer@student.tgm.ac.at

Project Repository: https://github.com/TGM-HWI-SWP/SWP_Discord_Bot_EMP